@host = http://localhost:5288

### Login (token oling). Javobdagi "token" ni quyidagi @token ga qo'ying.
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@markaz.uz",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Token (yuqoridagi login javobidan nusxa oling)
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Joriy foydalanuvchi
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin dashboard
GET {{host}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### O'quvchilar
GET {{host}}/api/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Guruhlar
GET {{host}}/api/admin/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sozlamalar (davomat sabablari, sintetik davrlar)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Jurnal ustunlari (dars sanalari)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/journal/columns?classId=c1&subjectId=sb1&quarter=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Guruh ko'rsatkichlari
GET {{host}}/api/admin/classes/c1/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
